tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE JoinTablesForNeuralNetworkTraining (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_1_id INT,
    dataset_2_id INT,
    dataset_3_id INT,
    dataset_4_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE neural_network_training (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset1_id INT NOT NULL,
    dataset2_id INT NOT NULL,
    dataset3_id INT NOT NULL,
    training_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset1_id INT,
    dataset2_id INT,
    dataset3_id INT,
    neural_network_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset1_id) REFERENCES dataset1(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset2_id) REFERENCES dataset2(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset3_id) REFERENCES dataset3(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (neural_network_id) REFERENCES neural_network(id)
);
